1
00:00:03,465 --> 00:00:05,083
当初同我来这的男人
The man I came here with

2
00:00:05,107 --> 00:00:07,868
是一个可靠而有志气的外交官
was a dependable, ambitious diplomat.

3
00:00:08,165 --> 00:00:09,752
你是怎么了?
What's happening to you?

4
00:00:10,396 --> 00:00:12,437
必须找人取代该亚法
Caiaphas who must be replaced.

5
00:00:12,476 --> 00:00:16,035
要是没手腕 就别搞政治游戏
Don't play politics unless you're good at it.

6
00:00:16,371 --> 00:00:22,479
即使面前是刀山火海 我们仍要无畏前行
We must push away our fear as we recognize the persecution we face.

7
00:00:22,838 --> 00:00:23,983
我是扫罗
I'm Saul.

8
00:00:24,017 --> 00:00:25,818
我来扫除这些渎神者
I have come to remove these blasphemers.

9
00:00:25,853 --> 00:00:28,454
用尽一切办法
Do whatever is necessary.

10
00:00:30,057 --> 00:00:31,257
尽量拿上行李!
Take what you can!

11
00:00:31,291 --> 00:00:34,594
我才不会被这个男人和他的威胁所吓倒
I will not be cowed by this man and his threats.

12
00:00:34,628 --> 00:00:36,696
这是我的土地 我要留下来
This was my land. I'm staying.

13
00:00:36,730 --> 00:00:38,764
- 还有我  - 我们耶路撒冷见
- And me.  - See you in Jerusalem.

14
00:00:38,799 --> 00:00:40,533
那里! 抓住他!
There! Take him!

15
00:00:40,567 --> 00:00:41,734
不!
No!

16
00:00:41,768 --> 00:00:43,936
我要毁了你!
I will crush you!

17
00:00:43,971 --> 00:00:46,706
放马过来!
You will try!

